     <p>The Forge has been established for over 40 years, priding ourselves  on making quality products for all our customers.  We have a very experienced team accustomed to handling both traditional and modern styles on any size project.
       
     Based in Swansea, The Forge is a national company with works all across the country.</p>
     <p>You will see photos of our products which will help you in choosing the right style, or if you wish, design your own gates and railings.  The only limitations are your imagination and the practical possibilities.       </p>
     <p>All our work is galvanised and you never have to worry about rusting.  There are also options of powder coating for that extra finishing touch.       </p>
     <p>As well as gates and railing we also manufacture fire escapes, spiral staircases, access staircases all to local current building regulations and naturally to suit any particular requirements you may have.   </p>
